            "text": "We fitted the meteorological data and influenza mortality data from 2002 to 2009 in a Susceptible - Infected - Recovered model . <S>",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "From the results , air temperature was a common significant driver of seasonal patterns",
